Oh, Tuan Venkateshwara!

00:11:02.450 --> 00:11:03.283
Siapa dia?

00:11:09.241 --> 00:11:10.116
Ini..

00:11:10.617 --> 00:11:13.408
Begitu banyak pesan tidak senonoh..

00:11:13.908 --> 00:11:16.158
Siapa yang mengirimkan ini padamu?

00:11:17.575 --> 00:11:18.617
Kenapa kamu diam?

00:11:19.033 --> 00:11:20.116
aku bertanya padamu

